## Tensor nodes.

-/

/-- The definitional tensor node relation for `coContrUnit`. -/
lemma tensorNode_coContrUnit : {δ' | μ ν}ᵀᵀ.tensor = (TensorTree.constTwoNodeE complexLorentzTensor
    Color.down Color.up Lorentz.coContrUnit).tensor:= by
  rfl

